des:
VAVA HOME products help you to control you ip camera. With this skill，user can connect VAVA HOME IP camera and see the camera video through alexa device(such as echoshow).
To use this skill, you had to do some simple steps as follow:
1.Download vavahome app from app store;
2.Register a account in vavahome app;
3.You need some "VAVAHOME" ipc devices in hand;
4.Download amazon "alexa" app from app store;
5.Config Echo with "Alexa" app;
6.Search vavahome skill from the Alexa skills category;
7.Click Enable skill of "VAVAHOME", and you'll be navigated to App name login page;
8.Input your VAVAHOME account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
9.Now all setup is finished;

You can enjoy you voice control you VAVAHOME IPC camera like this(front door is camera name):
1.Alexa, show my front door camera;
2.Alexa, turn off my front door camera;
